Please stop it!

258
00:17:25,290 --> 00:17:27,020
I can sleep on my own!

259
00:17:27,500 --> 00:17:29,560
I'm not poking fun.

260
00:17:30,410 --> 00:17:34,280
I'm merely doing what's necessary
as the owner of my closet.

261
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:40,180
You can just think of me as nothing 
more than a big hot water bottle.

262
00:17:41,900 --> 00:17:44,010
<i>That's easy for you to say...</i>

263
00:17:44,010 --> 00:17:45,540
<i>But the person at my back right now...</i>

264
00:17:46,040 --> 00:17:47,690
<i>is the most beautiful girl at school,</i>

265
00:17:47,690 --> 00:17:50,920
<i>wearing nothing but her school uniform, 
with no bra or panties...</i>

266
00:17:50,920 --> 00:17:53,800
<i>Not thinking about that is impossible!</i>

267
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:56,930
<i>What are you going to do 
if I get some weird idea?!</i>

268
00:17:56,930 --> 00:17:59,620
<i>Or is that also part of you making fun of me?!</i>

269
00:17:59,620 --> 00:18:01,340
<i>I don't get it.</i>

270
00:18:01,340 --> 00:18:03,810
<i>I don't understand what you're thinking!</i>

271
00:18:04,420 --> 00:18:07,020
There's one thing I'd like to tell you.

272
00:18:07,620 --> 00:18:11,470
I think I might have gone a bit too far teasing you.

273
00:18:12,300 --> 00:18:14,820
Regarding your physical condition, too.

274
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:17,470
I might not have been thoughtful enough.

275
00:18:18,250 --> 00:18:19,430
I'm sorry.

276
00:18:24,450 --> 00:18:25,840
What are you—

277
00:18:26,330 --> 00:18:27,830
Oxytocin.

278
00:18:28,710 --> 00:18:30,250
When skin touches skin,

279
00:18:30,250 --> 00:18:33,150
oxytocin is released and helps you relax.

280
00:18:33,150 --> 00:18:35,670
This should help you fall asleep easier.

281
00:18:35,670 --> 00:18:38,430
I'm going so far to help you.

282
00:18:38,430 --> 00:18:41,890
You'd best fall asleep instead 
of thinking about pointless stuff.

283
00:18:42,730 --> 00:18:46,390
Otherwise I'll have you sent to the trash heap.

284
00:18:47,060 --> 00:18:53,440
<i>Those words were quite typical for her 
as the owner of a closet.</i>

285
00:18:54,530 --> 00:18:58,830
<i>But I faintly but surely 
heard her say "I'm sorry."</i>

286
00:18:59,290 --> 00:19:04,900
<i>And though I had my face buried in the chest 
of the most beautiful girl at school,</i>

287
00:19:04,900 --> 00:19:07,580
<i>I didn't feel aroused. Instead, I felt safe.</i>

288
00:19:08,570 --> 00:19:13,440
<i>Maybe she really did worry about me.</i>

289
00:19:14,130 --> 00:19:16,000
<i>That thought made me realize...</i>

290
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:20,680
<i>that the goddess of the school 
and the owner of the closet...</i>

291
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:26,010
<i>President Takamine Takane, 
was also a human girl.</i>

292
00:19:27,700 --> 00:19:30,480
Do you think you'll be able to sleep, Shirota-kun?

293
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:32,940
Yes.

294
00:19:38,250 --> 00:19:41,340
May I ask you something?

295
00:19:41,340 --> 00:19:42,610
What is it?

296
00:19:43,020 --> 00:19:46,160
When you're being nice to me,

297
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:49,130
is that the carrot part of the carrot and stick?

298
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:52,330
Or do you have some...

299
00:19:52,830 --> 00:19:54,640
W-Well...

300
00:19:56,700 --> 00:19:58,280
What about you?

301
00:19:58,690 --> 00:20:00,500
Which would make you happier?

302
00:20:06,410 --> 00:20:08,010
Shirota-kun?

303
00:20:16,550 --> 00:20:19,450
Sleep well, Shirota-kun.

304
00:20:27,720 --> 00:20:28,750
Let's go over there!

305
00:20:28,750 --> 00:20:29,610
Yeah!

306
00:20:28,750 --> 00:20:30,160
Wait up!

307
00:20:57,560 --> 00:20:59,520
<i></i><i></i><i>Milk for Her and Him</i>

308
00:21:09,410 --> 00:21:10,580
I'm home.

309
00:21:13,350 --> 00:21:16,860
...is that the carrot part of the carrot and stick?

310
00:21:16,860 --> 00:21:18,060
Or do you...

311
00:21:21,570 --> 00:21:22,800
Oh, Kuro.

312
00:21:22,800 --> 00:21:23,640
Come here.

313
00:21:26,880 --> 00:21:28,140
Sheesh.

314
00:21:29,340 --> 00:21:33,670
Does he really think I'd go that far 
for someone I don't care about?

315
00:21:34,890 --> 00:21:36,600
Don't you agree?

316
00:21:41,860 --> 00:21:43,140
President?

317
00:21:44,190 --> 00:21:47,630
<i>You seem to be sound asleep, 
so I'll go home for today.</i>

318
00:21:47,630 --> 00:21:53,540
<i>There's still rice porridge in the fridge, 
so please eat it when you get hungry.</i>

319
00:21:53,540 --> 00:21:54,710
<i>Get well soon.</i>

320
00:21:56,370 --> 00:21:57,220
Hot!

321
00:21:58,760 --> 00:22:03,750
<i>The president today was a little...</i>

322
00:22:06,300 --> 00:22:08,410
<i>I feel like my fever's 
about to come back.</i>

